{"tid":970687,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"「梅窩食堂」BBQ爐煮湯圓","createTime":"2019-01-06T05:01:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-09T08:12:35.000Z","uid":209308,"like":56,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e17dff72cf556a3d8d9e79bf52533f49c4260f68","tid":970687,"uid":209308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:01:10.000Z","msg":"話說小弟我聖誕同班friend入左梅窩玩。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aR96BYi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaR96BYi.jpg&h=efff4e57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vBjuzK0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvBjuzK0.jpg&h=efb3c9e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n晏晝去左睇瀑布行山，只能講係山明水秀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jk2v3Ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fjk2v3Ea.jpg&h=076b6bea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZEnPzLR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZEnPzLR.jpg&h=7733f4ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n既然租左渡假屋，夜晚既時候當然係喺房打邊爐啦!<br />\n<br />\n但係租主話因為消防條例唔俾我地喺房打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實明明係因為渡假屋樓下係邊爐店，諗住唔俾我地自己打邊爐焗我地落去食啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n逼於無奈下唯有用個天台嚟BBQ啦。<br />\n當我地食完野既時候，發現唔知點解有兩包湯圓剩低<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n炭仲剩低好多，我地又唔想浪費啲炭，又燒野食燒到興起<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 無錯!炭火爐煮湯開始!<br />\n<br />\n一開頭要解決既問題，就係煮既器皿!<br />\n<br />\n如果用翻渡假屋啲鐵碟鐵煲，挑戰性就太低喇，所以，我地首先要自制煮既器皿。<br />\n<br />\n第一，要防火，BBQ紙碟就唔洗諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第二，要傳熱快，錫紙Ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第三，要係盤型而且堅固，錫紙可以做到盤型不過唔夠堅固   好易煮煮下漏水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n手頭上既物資好貧乏，淨係得紙碟同錫紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗左一陣，突發奇想，<br />\n<br />\nWhy Not Both !?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gA9zUi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gA9zUi.jpg&h=fe0ce9e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用錫紙包住紙碟，外層錫紙防火又傳熱快，內層紙碟提供盤形骨架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n倒熱水落湯圓，再用錫紙做蓋等佢焗下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V6hjW8m.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV6hjW8m.jpg&h=340198da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8WtK8e2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8WtK8e2.jpg&h=c1d5a974&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n初成品<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1aqNmBj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1aqNmBj.jpg&h=1e85f581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QTwT1Bk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQTwT1Bk.jpg&h=44e87b63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於我地煮既係水晶湯圓，完成品本應該係咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZ1poP4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZ1poP4.jpg&h=361c67dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係對比一下，發現我地整既湯圓有兩個問題<br />\n<br />\n第一，完全唔通透，煮到粉白色咁<br />\n第二，水燒得唔夠熱，湯圓浸得太耐，所以口感好粉<br />\n<br />\n結果第一次既炭煮湯圓係唔成功既<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係，我地既固執令我地再次挑戰!唔成功唔訓教!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問題應該係温度唔夠高 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;試下唔用燒烤網直接放喺炭上面燒？&ldquo;其中一個frd隨口一句<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無錯，可一試!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VZZeL7a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVZZeL7a.jpg&h=9cfa07a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/29fp8kx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F29fp8kx.jpg&h=7c001f8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gPOrCdT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgPOrCdT.jpg&h=f4f3f4c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路煮，我地七條友一路接力撥火，令個火一直keep住燒得旺<br />\n<br />\n大約8分鐘，終於有起息<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rXzuz1s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrXzuz1s.jpg&h=b6c0e7bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一粒通透既成品出現!!!!!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/84jqSOx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F84jqSOx.jpg&h=db851b01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BVXge1T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBVXge1T.jpg&h=c07626f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2otvjtz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2otvjtz.jpg&h=514492a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然好無聊亦好無謂，不過好難忘。<br />\n<br />\n一班frd，一齊為左一件on9事去討論去諗去試。<br />\n<br />\n好值得記念，所以開個post記錄下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝咁多位巴絲睇到呢度。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2ddeeb21da4a77d564d5a57bfb8f9b3b9a11e2","tid":970687,"uid":12628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-06T05:05:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa403f79c4f078ee8bd075e219b857003c7e9384","tid":970687,"uid":203931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"ching隻手好正 互射Ok?"},{"pid":"ed2c1d51f3fab614592b27980b93f9e1b7d10c13","tid":970687,"uid":8439,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"環保撚全面進場"},{"pid":"0f6c2f2f816dbf46d80edcd3d1d933dc1f4c64a3","tid":970687,"uid":205804,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fa403f79c4f078ee8bd075e219b857003c7e9384","tid":970687,"uid":203931,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"ching隻手好正 互射Ok?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:49:59.000Z","msg":"可唔可以幫我打？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e8bd1bf645f6ed27937a1e2eda1eb4501d6881","tid":970687,"uid":143288,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T03:54:30.000Z","msg":"睇前個樣&rarr;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇後個樣&rarr;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"143d47327beeb6d599787d507d59edf03bffdf6f","tid":970687,"uid":26976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-0