gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T05:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好鳩噏先，你邊度見到我對腳啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a27cb310632f4ed8e52e34ed9cdf572e1ef00ff3","tid":970687,"uid":138482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:07:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcd854c1c0c03d71f8e090c25ce47eb1a711daf","tid":970687,"uid":6845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:13:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e4bd554a16b11b86d6b9dfdf0d6541aada6ca7","tid":970687,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"請各位留手 唔好再推依個post 留返一片淨土比大家得閒放鬆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c676f1ce6c7bced36eaf89ceeeca5db756717741","tid":970687,"uid":22231,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:21:48.000Z","msg":"衰過facebook.."},{"pid":"55029467d3f91a5d29967d2d69afb0eed8e06086","tid":970687,"uid":209308,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"85e4bd554a16b11b86d6b9dfdf0d6541aada6ca7","tid":970687,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:16:26.000Z","msg":"請各位留手 唔好再推依個post 留返一片淨土比大家得閒放鬆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-09T06:41:32.000Z","msg":"有乜問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 完全唔明你意思<br />\n<br />\n明明個post重點係講梗BBQ湯圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淨乜土？"},{"pid":"e47a999503dcaa9a0cd96f6c1ac